OL,3,CGuernsey offers free tests for blood
OL,4,Cpressure and cholesterol
OL,6,FPeople in Guernsey will be offered
OL,7,Ffree health tests to check if they
OL,8,Fhave high blood pressure and
OL,9,Fcholesterol.
OL,11,FThe charity Guernsey Chest and Heart
OL,12,FLBG is working with Public Health to
OL,13,Frun the trial service from September
OL,14,Fto December.
OL,16,FThey hope to spot undiagnosed cases
OL,17,Fearly, as people can have no symptoms
OL,18,Fbut it can lead to serious problems
OL,19,Fsuch as heart attacks, strokes and
OL,20,Fdementia if not addressed.
