OL,6,FDr Nicola Brink, Director of Public
OL,7,FHealth, adds: "This is part of our
OL,8,Fprogramme to help islanders live
OL,9,Flonger and healthier lives.
OL,11,F"It is a great opportunity to reach
OL,12,Fmore people in the community,
OL,13,Fespecially those who might not realise
OL,14,Fthey are at risk. Early detection can
OL,15,Fmake a big difference to someone's
OL,16,Fhealth and quality of life."
OL,18,FCaroline Ogier, Manager of Guernsey
OL,19,FChest and Heart Centre, explains:
OL,20,F"These simple checks could prevent
OL,21,Fserious illness down the line.
