OL,6,F"We will be looking to extend this
OL,7,Fprogramme to Alderney residents, if
OL,8,Fthe pilot is successful."
OL,10,FThe checks will be carried out
OL,11,Falongside the existing five-yearly
OL,12,Fscreening programme at the Princess
OL,13,FElizabeth Hospital Chest and Heart
OL,14,FCentre, with no appointment or
OL,15,Freferral needed.
OL,17,FThe free drop-in clinics start in
OL,18,FSeptember on Monday and Wednesday
OL,19,Fafternoons from 1:15pm to 5pm, and
OL,20,FSaturday mornings from 8:30am to
OL,21,F12:00pm.
